{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"13334","heading":"Nonfuel use of coal","label":"13334 Nonfuel use of coal","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch134/schVI/ptA","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Program","label":"a Program","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"production of coke and other carbon products derived from coal;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"production of coal-derived, carbon-based chemical intermediates that are precursors of value-added chemicals and polymers;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"production of chemicals from coal-derived synthesis gas;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"coal treatment processes, including methodologies such as solvent-extraction techniques that produce low ash, low sulfur, coal-based chemical feedstocks; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"waste utilization, including recovery, processing, and marketing of products derived from sulfur, carbon dioxide, nitrogen, and ash from coal.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Plan contents","label":"b Plan contents","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the known and potential processes for using coal in the creation of products in the chemical, utility, fuel, and carbon-based materials industries;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the costs, benefits, and economic feasibility of using coal products in the chemical and materials industries, including value-added chemicals, carbon-based products, coke, and waste derived from coal;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the economics of coproduction of products from coal in conjunction with the production of electric power, thermal energy, and fuel;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the economics of the refining of coal and coal byproducts to produce nonfuel products;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the economics of coal utilization in comparison with other feedstocks that might be used for the same purposes;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the steps that can be taken by the public and private sectors to bring about commercialization of technologies developed under the program recommended; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":null,"label":"7","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13334/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13334%2Fb%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the past development, current status, and future potential of coal products and processes associated with nonfuel uses of coal.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
